manasukketha maharasa ( tamil : மனசுக்கேத்த மகராசா ) is a 1989 indian tamil action drama thriller film , directed by dheenadhayaal and produced by a. r. santhilal nahar and s. gowri gurukkal . the film stars ramarajan , seetha , nizhalgal ravi and goundamani in lead roles . the film had musical score by deva who made his debut with this film .